# Integration Tests Directory

Place integration test files here following the naming convention:
- `*.integration.test.ts` for integration tests

Example structure:
```
tests/integration/
  api/
    auth.integration.test.ts
    messages.integration.test.ts
    rooms.integration.test.ts
    users.integration.test.ts
  database/
    prisma.integration.test.ts
    migrations.integration.test.ts
  redis/
    cache.integration.test.ts
    pubsub.integration.test.ts
  websocket/
    socket.integration.test.ts
```

Integration tests require external services:
- PostgreSQL (localhost:5433 or TEST_DATABASE_URL)
- Redis (localhost:6380 or TEST_REDIS_URL)

Run with: `npm run test:integration`
